    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total dream! This car is in pristine, showroom condition. It\u2019s been pampered in a garage, meticulously detailed, and honestly looks and smells brand new. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I can\u2019t wait for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
