      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is practically flawless\u2014inside and out, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with every single detail, so it runs like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
