    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This 996.2-generation wide-body features the venerable 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six paired with a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the IMS bearing and Rear Main Seal have been proactively upgraded with LN Engineering components. The viscous multi-plate clutch AWD system provides exceptional lateral grip, complemented by a factory-spec suspension that retains its original damping rates and bushing compliance. The exterior shows uniform paint meter readings across all panels, and the interior cockpit remains free of typical soft-touch delamination or bolster fatigue. A technically flawless example of the final analog 911 era, ready for a discerning collector.",
